1157922483.text: "In vitro kinase inhibition profile showed that Foretinib suppressed c-MET, RON, VEGFRs, c-KIT, FLT-3, platelet derived growth factor receptors (PDGFRs) and TIE-2 while it exhibited less effect on fibroblast growth factor receptor 1 (FGFR1) and epidermal growth factor receptor (EGFR)."
